root: ^Ha! I can't believe you actually did it!
^When you said you'd do it, I thought to myself, I said, "There's no way a dame like that would take the time of day to do such a favor for ol' Jerry!"
^I said "If she really does clean up that mess for me, I might just-" huh?
^Oh, right, right, a deal's a deal.
^Check upstairs. There's a new playspace up there for the kiddies, maybe your boy is up there.
^Here, I'll cut up one of those bits of tape blocking the escalator.
^And, hey, if you're ever looking for work... There's always room for a tall glass like you around here.
